zofu
------------------------------------------
Zofu (Zofu is Object-oriented Fortran Unit-testing) is a framework for carrying
out unit testing of Fortran code modules. As the name suggests, it makes use of
the object-oriented features of Fortran 2003.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.5.4-1
  libgfortran5-12.4.0-3
  libopenmpifh40-4.1.6-1
  libzofu-devel-1.1.1-1bl2
  libzofu1-1.1.1-1bl2
  pkg-config-2.3.0-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  binutils-2.43.1-1
  cygport-0.36.9-1
  gcc-core-12.4.0-3
  gcc-fortran-12.4.0-3
  libopenmpi-devel-4.1.6-1
  meson-1.3.2-1
  ninja-1.12.0-1

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/acroucher/zofu

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/acroucher/zofu/archive/refs/tags/v1.1.1.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack zofu-1.1.1-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./zofu-1.1.1-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/zofu-1.1.1-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/zofu-1.1.1-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libzofu1-1.1.1-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libzofu-devel-1.1.1-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(zofu)
  /usr/bin/zofu-driver.exe
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/zofu.README
  /usr/share/doc/zofu/LICENSE
  /usr/share/doc/zofu/README.md

(libzofu1)
  /usr/bin/cygzofu-1.dll

(libzofu-devel)
  /usr/include/zofu.mod
  /usr/include/zofu_kinds.mod
  /usr/include/zofu_mpi.mod
  /usr/include/zofu_scan.mod
  /usr/include/zofu_str_utils.mod
  /usr/lib/libzofu.dll.a
  /usr/lib/pkgconfig/zofu.pc

